This is a prototype implementation of the Indexing example in the 'Getting started guide' of Xapian in R language. (http://getting-started-with-xapian.readthedocs.org/en/latest/practical_example/indexing/index.html).

****Latest development version of xapian should be installed (xapian-1.3)

****Installing the package [Note: these examples have only been tested in the developed machine. In case if an issue arises during installation, please contact me at amandajayanetti@gmail.com for guidance and/or assistance to build it from source.]


****If devtools is not already installed [install.packages("devtools")]

library(devtools)
install_github("amandaJayanetti/xapianExamples")

****Index-Plan

db<-c("path/to/DB")

data<-c("path/to/data")

id<-c(0)

indexFields <-list( list(2,"S","Title"), list(8,"XD","Description"))

xapian_index(db,data,id,indexFields,"en")


****Inspecting the database

xapian_inspectDB(db)
